# Raw .mov clips dropped into the moods folder are typically huge (hundreds
# of MB direct from screen-recordings). They should be transcoded to .mp4
# via scripts/seamless-moods.mjs before tracking. Excluded by default so
# `git add .` doesn't accidentally try to push a half-gig file past
# GitHub's 100 MB hard limit.
